  "prompt": "How do I make clothes in Roblox?",
  "response": "Creating clothes in Roblox involves designing and uploading your custom clothing items to the platform. Here\u2019s a step-by-step guide to help you make clothes in Roblox:\n\n---\n\n### **Step 1: Prepare Your Design**\n1. **Understand Roblox Clothing Templates**:\n   - Roblox provides templates for shirts, pants, t-shirts, and jackets.\n   - Download the official Roblox templates from the **[Roblox Creator Hub](https://create.roblox.com/docs/art/accessories/classic-clothing)**.\n\n2. **Design Your Clothing**:\n   - Use graphic design software like **Adobe Photoshop**, **GIMP**, or **Paint.NET** to create your design.\n   - Import the Roblox template into your software and design over it.\n   - Follow the guidelines on the template to avoid issues when uploading.\n\n---\n\n### **Step 2: Save Your Design**\n1. Save your design as a `.png` file.\n2. Ensure the file size meets Roblox requirements:\n   - Maximum size: 1024x1024 pixels.\n   - Maximum file size: 10 MB.\n\n---\n\n### **Step 3: Upload Your Clothing**\n1. Log in to your **[Roblox Account](https://www.roblox.com/)**.\n2. Go to the **Create** section and click **Develop** (or visit **[Create](https://create.roblox.com/)** directly).\n3. Click on **Shirts**, **Pants**, **T-Shirts**, or **Jackets**, depending on what you\u2019re uploading.\n4. Click **Choose File** and upload your `.png` design.\n5. Name your clothing item and add a description.\n\n---\n\n### **Step 4: Publish and Sell (Optional)**\n1. Set a price for your clothing if you want to sell it (requires a Roblox Premium subscription).\n2. Click **Upload** to publish your clothing item.\n3. Your clothing will now be available in your inventory or the Roblox Catalog (if made public).\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Success**\n- **Test Your Design**: Use Roblox Studio to preview how your clothing looks on avatars.\n- **Check for Quality**: Ensure your design is high-quality and follows Roblox\u2019s guidelines.\n- **Stay Creative**: Experiment with unique designs to stand out.\n\n---\n\nBy following these steps, you can create and upload your own custom clothing in Roblox!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
